		"description": "<p>At 17th level, you have mastered the pinnacle of your craft. Once per day, you may use your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.9jRexTqxAQjW2snB]{Potent Brew} feature to create one @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-adventuring-gear.Item.wrvoldjxwhogx3ea]{Healing Potion (Supreme)}. You may only create one, but unlike other potions created by your Potent Brew, it does not spoil.</p><p>Additionally, once per day you may expend one use of your Channel Divinity to cast the spell feeblemind. This also counts as a cleric spell for you and may be prepared alongside your spells as normal.</p>",
